We understand the base conversion, binary digits and the powerful binary search algorithm.

You can experience it here: https://hryanjones.com/guess-my-word 
But there is also a more popular game called Wordle now.

And if you want to see how it works: https://learningcontent.cisco.com/games/binary/index.html

We can represent any type of information using binary digits, also known as bits. Bits are the
fundamental building blocks for any machine, including your laptop, smartphone, and calculator.
